Install and require all the necessary packages.
set up the env file while adding all the necessary env variales to it.
connect with the mongoose database
create your schema then model
write an api with the post method to create new user
write code to check if user already exists, if so, send message, if not create new user.
write an api with the post method to log in user details into the database.
With a get method, write an api that fetches the log from the database.
